  "detailed_description": "<strong>Mushroom Path</strong> is a 2D difficult precision platformer where you try to pass levels while collecting things and trying to avoid enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/0596da42548b931f609fce34cdca5189.avif?t=1751562806\" width=608 height=64 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/9aa8683cf243f6d66d426b58c16b2996.webp?t=1751562806\" width=586 height=34 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No story:</strong> There is no story, just run, jump, collect.<br></li><li><strong>4 Seasons and over 100+ levels to pass: </strong> Different seasons different things to encounter. Can you pass all of them ?<br></li><li><strong>Different abilities to play!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Power-ups: </strong> Collect power-ups you see along the way to help you, strengthen them with the coins you collected , reach more levels with their help.<br></li><li><strong>Colorful mushrooms: </strong> Need an extra challange ? Try collecting mushrooms of different colors.<br></li><li><strong>Over 50+ achievements to complete!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Controller support!</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.poster.avif?t=1751562806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.webm?t=1751562806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.mp4?t=1751562806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Mushroom Path</strong> is a 2D difficult precision platformer where you try to pass levels while collecting things and trying to avoid enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/0596da42548b931f609fce34cdca5189.avif?t=1751562806\" width=608 height=64 /></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/9aa8683cf243f6d66d426b58c16b2996.webp?t=1751562806\" width=586 height=34 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>No story:</strong> There is no story, just run, jump, collect.<br></li><li><strong>4 Seasons and over 100+ levels to pass: </strong> Different seasons different things to encounter. Can you pass all of them ?<br></li><li><strong>Different abilities to play!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Power-ups: </strong> Collect power-ups you see along the way to help you, strengthen them with the coins you collected , reach more levels with their help.<br></li><li><strong>Colorful mushrooms: </strong> Need an extra challange ? Try collecting mushrooms of different colors.<br></li><li><strong>Over 50+ achievements to complete!</strong><br></li><li><strong>Controller support!</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.poster.avif?t=1751562806\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.webm?t=1751562806\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537070/extras/83ef8701762b4470f4bd03a7ee04a088.mp4?t=1751562806\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
